message.body: Hey ##### Text me back if you get this message. We're in LA! Yeah! Jam
Fantastic. Can't wait to see you. Glad we can contact you. Sof is doing well. She can't wait to see you. We're going to pick you up from the airport on Wednesday. J&S
I don't suppose you know what the Everton v Arsenal score was? I was on the plane so missed the game.
Blues 3 gunners 0. I hope you have your little victory celebration before I get there.
Oh really. What a stupendous result for the mighty blues. I'll save my victory celebration for your arrival. Whoop whoop!
This time tomorrow I'll be on my way to see you!
Can't wait. Sofie is so excited, she did a little wee.
